    "title": "Bombay Shaving Company is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Junior)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Bombay Shaving Company! We are hiring a E-commerce Executive for our Coimbatore team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Bombay Shaving Company:\nBombay Shaving Company is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bombay Shaving Company!",
